# General Canonicalization Rules (Priority Order)
# Purpose: Handle Protocol + WWW + Extension inconsistencies in a SINGLE redirection.

# 1. http + www + .html -> https + root + name
http://www.igrs.online/*.html https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 2. http + www -> https + root
http://www.igrs.online/* https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 3. http + .html -> https + name
http://igrs.online/*.html https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 4. http -> https
http://igrs.online/* https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 5. https + www + .html -> https + name
https://www.igrs.online/*.html https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 6. https + www -> https + root
https://www.igrs.online/* https://igrs.online/:splat 301

# 7. https + .html -> https + name (Cleanup for internal links/direct access on correct domain)
/*.html /:splat 301
